features: [All in One] The whole glitter tattoo kit includes 36 colours glitter (6 fluorescence), 207 stencils 4 brushes and 3 glue. One set will meet all your need. Your kids can use this glitter tattoo kit to complete a beautiful tattoo.

[Skin-Friendly & Non-Toxic] This glitter tattoo kit is made of safe and non-toxic material, which will not harm to sensitive skin. The temporary tattoo is easy to remove with soap and warm water. (Everyone's skin is different. Test on a small area of skin for allergy before use.)

[Reusable Tattoo Stencils] Our glitter tattoo stencils are specially designed into different theme, such as animals, mermaid, fairy, astronaut and so on. Both boys and girls can enjoy to make their own temporary tattoo.

[Must for Festival] Some kids want to beautify themselves on some festivals or special days, such as Christmas, Halloween, birthdays or school party day. Our glitter tattoo kit make your kid the most shinning one at parties!
[Gifts for All Age Kids] Perfect gifts to satisfy kids’ curiosity and cultivate aesthetic ability and practical ability.
